node.text: Amazing racing today! Times were tight, so tight that second feels kinda shit. But hey still a great result and better than crashing in the first turn! 😂 fired up for Lousa! This is such weird year and season but congrats to all the boys for putting on a good show! Now going to bed for five days to recover from this. Bravo mon @lorisvergier #batard 😂

node.text:
Too much #COD geeking these days... 😂
I’m giving a solid 30-45 minutes work out Tomorrow 11AM Paris time on my YouTube channel, try to win a pair of @crankbrothers #Superbruni #MalletDH by taking a pic and tagging both me and @crankbrothers. They will pick the winners. Link in bio. 🇫🇷- Trop de Call Of en ce moment... Demain 11h, je vous fais un petit work out qui va déchirer. Taggez moi et @crankbrothers sur votre photo suivant le live de demain pour essayer de gagner une paire de pédales #superbruni #malletDh! 
À demain !!

node.text: Pour les Français 🇫🇷 : vendredi je suis votre coach ! Spinning class et posez moi vos questions !! Si vous avez un home trainer et voulez pédaler avec moi, vous me rejoignez live sur Instagram et on tue un peu le temps. Je repondrai à des questions si vous en avez! Courage à tout ceux qui restent à la maison ! À vendredi 👊💪

node.text: Duuuuur ! First day on the national champs track was touuuugh. Not much flow or grip so it will be hard to not find the limits 😂. Rain has arrived, again...

node.text:
Les Gets never disappoints ! Even though we couldn’t fight for the win, I had an amazing day just thanks to the spectators, I missed you guys so much. Downhill is the best and after this track and crowd, I’m so proud to be French 😍.
🇫🇷 : Les Gets nous a encore fait vibrer !! Dommage pour les conditions mais le public était incroyable, je vous kiffe merci beaucoup ! Fier d’être français. Bravo à @thibautdaprela qui a représenté le pays comme il faut, à l’année prochaine 🙌
📸 Seb Schieck

node.text:
Our turn tomorrow! It’s been a relaxed week so far, no seeding, no qualies, just that one run 💪.
I still need to figure out some sections and it should be good to go! Time to keep building the confidence 🔥 - Photos by SSchieck

@gopro #quik #pov

node.text: Round 1 was brutal, managed to bring home a top 10 and that was the goal. So fun to see the whole circuit again. Impressed by the pace of the top guys this weekend, I didn’t have that in store, not yet. Stoked for Troy ! The overall hunt is on !! The track was tough for everybody, good job to everyone racing 🙌. @crankworx time now 🔥 - PC @michalcervenyphoto
